'''Nectarwine''' was a fermented [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] drink from [[Nepoy]], in the [[Senex sector/Legends|Senex sector]]. Seven hundred barrels of this beverage were served at the wedding feast of [[Gorga Desilijic Aarrpo/Legends|Gorga]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] and [[Anachro]] the [[H'uun]].

Nectarwine clotted and curdled if subjected to rough treatment, which gave it an appalling taste. It was a contraband item in that sale of it outside of the [[Juvex sector/Legends|Juvex]] and Senex sectors was forbidden by those sectors' authorities, which led to a thriving black market in vintages of nectarwine.<ref name="TEA">''[[The Essential Atlas]]''</ref>

